### Aurelia API — Phase 2 transversal collection
### VS Code REST Client

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@fileId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
@evidenceId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000002
@entityId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000003
@workflowDefinitionId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000004
@workflowInstanceId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000005
@workflowStepId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000006

# ──────────────────────────────────────────────
# Files
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────

### Upload file
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/files/upload
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=Boundary

--Boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="sample.txt"
Content-Type: text/plain

Archivo de prueba Aurelia
--Boundary--

### Get file metadata
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/files/{{fileId}}

# ──────────────────────────────────────────────
# Evidences
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────

### Create evidence
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/evidences
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Evidencia de prueba",
  "description": "Evidencia transversal para validar Fase 2",
  "evidenceType": "photo",
  "fileId": "{{fileId}}",
  "latitude": -33.4489,
  "longitude": -70.6693
}

### List evidences
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/evidences

### List evidences by entity
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/evidences?entityType=inspection&entityId={{entityId}}

### Link evidence to entity
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/evidences/{{evidenceId}}/link
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "entityType": "inspection",
  "entityId": "{{entityId}}"
}

### Validate evidence
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/evidences/{{evidenceId}}/validate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "validated",
  "validationNotes": "Evidencia revisada correctamente"
}

# ──────────────────────────────────────────────
# Comments
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────

### Create comment
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/comments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "entityType": "inspection",
  "entityId": "{{entityId}}",
  "body": "Comentario de prueba para entidad transversal",
  "isInternal": true
}

### List comments by entity
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/comments?entityType=inspection&entityId={{entityId}}

# ──────────────────────────────────────────────
# Audit
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────

### List audit logs
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/audit

### List audit logs by entity
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/audit?entityType=inspection&entityId={{entityId}}

# ──────────────────────────────────────────────
# Workflows
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────

### List workflow definitions
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/workflows/definitions

### Create workflow definition
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/workflows/definitions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "code": "WF-TEST-INSPECTION",
  "name": "Workflow de prueba inspección",
  "description": "Workflow temporal para validar creación manual",
  "entityType": "inspection",
  "isActive": true,
  "steps": [
    {
      "stepOrder": 1,
      "code": "REVIEW",
      "name": "Revisión",
      "slaHours": 24
    }
  ]
}

### Start workflow instance
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/workflows/start
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "workflowDefinitionId": "{{workflowDefinitionId}}",
  "entityType": "inspection",
  "entityId": "{{entityId}}"
}

### Start workflow with mismatched entity type should return 400
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/workflows/start
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "workflowDefinitionId": "{{workflowDefinitionId}}",
  "entityType": "incident",
  "entityId": "{{entityId}}"
}

### Advance workflow step
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/workflows/{{workflowInstanceId}}/advance
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "stepId": "{{workflowStepId}}",
  "action": "approve",
  "notes": "Paso aprobado"
}

### List workflow instances
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/workflows

### List workflow instances by entity
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/workflows?entityType=inspection&entityId={{entityId}}
